<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="its-a-pleasure-its-my-pleasure">it's a pleasure / (it's) my pleasure</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>[用于对别人感谢的回答] 别客气；没什么：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Thank you for coming to help us. 
谢谢你来帮助我们。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— It’s a pleasure. / My pleasure.
别客气。</p></div></div>